    Reliable info:
    Guests say the description and photos for this property are very accurate.

    Attic Apartment 468 Sagrada Familia is located in Barcelona, just 1.6 miles from Nova Icaria Beach and 1.8 miles from Bogatell Beach. Guests staying at this apartment have access to free Wifi and a terrace. Sagrada Familia is a 5-minute walk from the apartment and La Pedrera is 1.2 miles away. The air-conditioned apartment consists of 1 bedroom, a living room, a fully equipped kitchen with a dishwasher and a coffee machine, and 1 bathroom with a walk-in shower and a hair dryer. Towels and bed linen are provided in the apartment. The property has an outdoor dining area. The apartment has a picnic area where you can spend the day outdoors. Casa Batllo is 1.4 miles from the apartment, while Passeig de Gracia is 1.5 miles away. The nearest airport is Barcelona-El Prat Airport, 9.3 miles from Attic Apartment 468 Sagrada Familia.

    Couples in particular like the location – they rated it 9.6 for a two-person trip.
